{"id": "vos009", "name": "Audio_St34_702_12_29", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Panic"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_Far", "Explosion"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "That's coming from... A.R.C. headquarters? Squad B, report the situation.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member A"], "content": "<i>This is Squad B, the explosion came from A.R.C. headquarters. The academy looks like it's been damaged as well. It appears the Architects' primary targets are important structures in the Administration District.</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Damn, what the hell is that bastard doing...</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "Captain, I repeat: Architects are currently attacking the Administration District. Clearly, they're trying to cut off the people's resources... You said to trust that Simon Jackson could stop all this, but it's obviously only getting worse.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "You released him right in front of us. There was already a lot of internal objections, but everybody trusted your decision. It's about time you listen to us, huh? This demands immediate action!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "I agree, Captain. I don't know what sort of relationship you have with Simon, but we've been with you for a long time. How can you trust a fugitive on the run, but not us?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "You once told us that the power the Armed Forces holds was given to us by the people, and that using it is the only way to pay them back.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "I know, I...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_JOEZ", "Fierce Explosion"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "... <i>*cough*... *cough*</i>... What happened... Architects? This many!?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Step", "Mechnical Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "Cap-Captain!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Open fire!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢"], "content": "<i>......ˊ̨̨͘!̡͟͡%̶&̷̧̨͟͝......@̷̡̀͢^̷*̷̸̢̛͝&̧̨̛͘^̧́͘͠͏*̸......</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Damn... Squad A, listen up! I'm gonna flank from the left and create an opening. Head out as soon as you see an opportunity!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "There's no openings over there, Captain! Are you... going to sacrifice yourself!?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "As long as you still view me as your captain, then listen to me!\n<font size=\"3.6\">Get ready! Run!</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢"], "content": "<i>h̴́͢͡͝9͘͏̡0̡͘͞͞7̶̸̨͘̕T̷̷̸̸͠Y̴̢̢͡͝H̴̕͏8̶̢͜͟0̴̛͠=͠͝҉̛h̶̢̀̕͠……</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Huff... there's... too many...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">UURRGGGGHH!!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Boris!</font> What's wrong!? Hold on just a bit longer!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "... <i>*cough*</i>... I still see you as my captain... so I...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "Hey! Watch out!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Hacking", "Hacking"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "......!? Not moving?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hey, what you staring at? FIRE!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢"], "content": "<i>$̶%̴̸̨͠*̨_̵͡͠(͞͡͠͝_̸́……<font size=\"1.6\">ģ͟͏f̕̕6͘͡͏̶҉j̸̸̷͢-̨́͝……</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "What... what have you done?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Not bad. Simon's little toy... Just gotta press it and it'll paralyze a group of Architects.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "... I'm surprised that kind of technology exists...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hey, why are looking at me like that? Aren't we helping each other out? I can get the boys to bring your men to get treated...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Raises Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Wah! What the hell are you doing!?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "Captain! Calm down!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "... Get the f*** outta here!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Okay, okay! I'm leaving. Didn't get the message, geez...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... Damn...</font>\nBoris, Boris! Stay focused! We're gonna get you to a medical center immediately...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "Captain... we're... the Armed Forces... We've got to... protect the citizens...\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Shut up! Just shut up!\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member B"], "content": "Captain... you've got to make... <font size=\"1.6\">the right decision...</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "Boris! Boris is...\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......\nThe right decision...</font>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "Stands Up"], "content": ""}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Team Member C"], "content": "Captain\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "I'll win back... your trust.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Panic"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_Far", "爆発"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "あっちは……A.R.C.本部の方角か？\nB小隊！報告を！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 A"], "content": "<i>こちらB小隊。\n爆発位置はA.R.C.本部です。\nアカデミーにも被害が出ています。\nまた、アーキテクトが行政エリアの重要施設に対して攻撃している模様です！</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">くそっ！いったい何を企んで……</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "隊長、もう一度言います。\nアーキテクトは行政エリアに向かって攻撃を仕掛けています。\n市民の資源を断とうとしているんですよ。\n隊長は、Simon Jacksonが全てを阻止すると言いましたよね。\nでも、状況は明らかに悪化している。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "Simon Jacksonを逃がしたことについて、納得の行っていない者もたくさんいます。\nでも、みんなあんたを信じてる。\nたまにはこっちの言葉に耳を傾けてくれてもいいんじゃないか？\n今はもう一刻の猶予も許されないんだ！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "……自分も同じ考えです。\n隊長、あなたとSimonの関係も、お二人の過去も自分は存じません。\nでも、自分たちはずっとあなたについてきました。\n逃亡した犯罪者は信じるのに、自分たちのことは信じられないって言うんですか？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "俺たちの手にしている武力は、市民たちが俺たちに預けたものだって言ってたよな。\nそして、俺たちが唯一市民の信頼に応えるための手段でもあるって。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "わかってる。俺は……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_JOEZ", "激しい爆発"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "ゴホッ……ゴホッ……\n何があった！アーキテクト？この数は……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Step", "機械の足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "た、隊長！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "撃て！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢"], "content": "<i>......ˊ̨̨͘!̡͟͡%̶&̷̧̨͟͝......@̷̡̀͢^̷*̷̸̢̛͝&̧̨̛͘^̧́͘͠͏*̸......</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "くそっ……A小隊！\n俺が左へ向かって隙を作る！\nその間に逃げるんだ！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "左にスペースなんて……隊長！まさか……自分を犠牲にして俺たちを！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "俺のことをまだ隊長だと思うのなら言うことを聞け！\n<font size=\"3.6\">行くぞ！走れ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢"], "content": "<i>h̴́͢͡͝9͘͏̡0̡͘͞͞7̶̸̨͘̕T̷̷̸̸͠Y̴̢̢͡͝H̴̕͏8̶̢͜͟0̴̛͠=͠͝҉̛h̶̢̀̕͠……</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "はぁ……っ……\n数が……多すぎる……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重たい衝撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">ぐあああああ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Boris！</font>おい！なんで！しっかりしろ！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "ゴホッ……お、前を……隊長だって思ってるか……ら……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "危ない！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Hacking", "ハッキング"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "……！？動きがとまった？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "おい！ボーっとしてないで撃てって！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢"], "content": "<i>$̶%̴̸̨͠*̨_̵͡͠(͞͡͠͝_̸́……<font size=\"1.6\">ģ͟͏f̕̕6͘͡͏̶҉j̸̸̷͢-̨́͝……</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "なにを……したんだ？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "おーまじで効果あったじゃん。\nSimonのおもちゃ……\nボタン押すだけでアーキテクトの動き止められるとかすげー。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "……そんな技術が……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "おいおい、なんでそんな目で俺のこと見んの？\n助け合い、だろ？\nもし必要なら、兄弟たちに隊員を治療に連れて行ってもらうけど……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "うわ！？なんで！？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "隊長！落ち着いて！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "……消えろ！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "わかったわかったから！\n今すぐ消えますって！\nよかれと思って助けたのにこの仕打ち……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……くそ……</font>\nBoris、Boris！しっかりするんだ！\nすぐに医療センターに……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "隊長……俺たちは……武装部隊だ……\n市民の……あんぜ……ん、を……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "もう話さなくていい！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "隊長……<font size=\"1.6\">正しい選択……を……</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "Boris！Borisは……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">………\n正しい選択、か……</font>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "立ち上がる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "隊長？\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "俺は……お前たちの信頼に応えてみせる……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Panic"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_Far", "爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "那個方向是……A.R.C. 總部？ B 小隊，立即回報狀況！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[隊員 A]"], "content": "<i>這裡是 B 小隊，爆炸地點確認為 A.R.C.總部。另外學院也有遭受破壞的跡象，研判建造者正以行政區重要設施為主進行攻擊。</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">可惡，那傢伙到底在搞什麼……</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "隊長，我要再說一次：建造者現在攻擊行政區，明顯是想斷絕民生的資源……你說相信 Simon Jackson 會阻止這一切，但顯然情況只是越來越惡化。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "你在我們面前放走 Simon Jackson，內部已經有許多異議，但大家都相信你的決定。這次該聽聽大家的了吧？情況已經刻不容緩！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "……我也這麼覺得。隊長，我不清楚你跟 Simon 有過什麼過去，但我們也跟著你很久了，難道你寧可相信一個逃亡的犯人，也不願意相信我們嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "你說過，我們武裝部隊手上所握有的武力是人民所交付的，也是我們唯一能回應的方式。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "這我知道，我……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_JOEZ", "劇烈爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "咳、咳……發生什麼事……建造者？這些數量！？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Step", "機械腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "隊、隊長！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "開槍！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢]"], "content": "<i>……ˊ̨̨͘!̡͟͡%̶&̷̧̨͟͝……@̷̡̀͢^̷*̷̸̢̛͝&̧̨̛͘^̧́͘͠͏*̸……</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "可惡……A 小隊聽令！我去左側製造機會，抓到時機就立刻逃出！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "左側根本沒有空隙……隊長！難道你……要犧牲自己嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "還當我是隊長的話，就聽我的！\n<font size=\"3.6\">預備！跑！</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢]"], "content": "<i>h̴́͢͡͝9͘͏̡0̡͘͞͞7̶̸̨͘̕T̷̷̸̸͠Y̴̢̢͡͝H̴̕͏8̶̢͜͟0̴̛͠=͠͝҉̛h̶̢̀̕͠……</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "呼……數量也……太多了……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">呃啊啊啊啊啊！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Boris！</font>你怎麼！？振作點！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "咳……就、就當你是隊長……所以才……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "你們！小心！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Hacking", "駭入"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "……！？不動了？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂，還愣在那裡幹什麼？快開槍啊！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[?̷̡͘͠?̨̢͟?̶̡͘?̶̢?̶͝?́͡͠?̸̛͢]"], "content": "<i>$̶%̴̸̨͠*̨_̵͡͠(͞͡͠͝_̸́……<font size=\"1.6\">ģ͟͏f̕̕6͘͡͏̶҉j̸̸̷͢-̨́͝……</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "你……你做了什麼？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "還真有用耶，Simon 留下的這玩意兒……只要按下去就能讓一群建造者癱瘓呢。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "……居然擁有那種技術……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂，幹嘛用那種眼神看我？我們不是在互相幫助嗎？需要的話，我可以叫黑幫的弟兄送你隊員去治療……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哇！你幹什麼！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "隊長！不要衝動！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "……給我滾！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "好、好！我走就是了，好心沒好報……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……可惡……</font>\nBoris、Boris！保持清醒！我們立刻送你到醫療中心……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "隊長……我們是……武裝部隊……必須要保護市民的……安全……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "先不要說那麼多話！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 B"], "content": "隊長……你得做出……<font size=\"1.6\">對的選擇……</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "Boris！Boris 他……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……。\n對的選擇嗎……</font>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "站立"], "content": ""}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["隊員 C"], "content": "隊長？\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "我會回應……你們的信任。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Panic"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_Far", "폭발"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "저 방향은......A.R.C. 본부?  B 소대, 즉시 상황을 보고하라!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["대원 A"], "content": "<i>여긴 B 소대, 폭발 지점이 A.R.C. 본부인 것으로 확인됐다. 그외 아카데미 역시 파괴된 흔적이 포착됐다. 아무래도 아키텍트가 행정구역의 주요 시설 위주로 파괴 행위를 벌인 것으로 판단된다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">제길, 그 녀석 대체 무슨 생각인 건지...</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["대원 B"], "content": "대장, 다시 한번 말할게. 아키텍트는 지금 행정구역을 공격하고 있어. 시민들의 자원 공급을 전부 차단시키려는 의도가 분명해.... Simon Jackson이 이 모든 것을 막아줄 거라고 믿었지? 하지만 상황은 더 악화되고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["대원 B"], "content": "우리들 앞에서 Simon Jackson을 놓아준 것은, 내부에서도 이미 말이 많은 상황이야. 하지만 모두들 네 결정을 믿어줬지. 이번엔 모두의 말을 들어줘야 하는 거 아니야? 상황은 이미 걷잡을 수 없게 됐다고!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["대원 C"], "content": "......저도 그렇게 생각합니다, 대장. 당신과  Simon 사이에 어떤 과거가 있었는지는 모르지만, 그래도 우리들은 당신을 오랜 시간동안 따라왔습니다. 설마 그런 우리들보다 그런 도망자 한 명을 더 신뢰한다는 겁니까?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["대원 B"], "content": "네가 말했었지? 우리 무장 부대가 가진 힘은 시민들을 위한 것이며 그들을 위해 쓰는 것이 유일한 보답 방식이라고 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "알고 있다. 나는...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explotion_JOEZ", "맹렬한 폭발